Detailed Description

A mapping from String values to various primitive types.

An Persistence provides a facility for saving different primitive value in one container which use different string to identify different primitive value.

 // Set action and int32_t value to Demand
 Persistence persistence;
 persistence.putInt("INT_VALUE", 1000);
 persistence.putString("STRING_VALUE", "this is a astring");
 int32_t int_value = persistence.getInt("INT_VALUE");
 String string_value = persistence.getString("STRING_VALUE");
